<hr /><h3>Contact us</h3>
<p>If you have questions, concerns or suggestions related to our Privacy Policy or our privacy practices, <a href="mailto:privacyoffice@verizon.com?subject=Verizon%20Privacy%20Policy%20question%2C%20concern%20or%20suggestion">e-mail us</a> or contact us at:</p>
<p>Verizon Privacy Office<br />1300 I Street, NW<br /><span style="letter-spacing: 0.2px;">Suite 500 East</span><br />Washington, DC 20005<br />Fax: 202-789-1432</p>
